          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "For ticketing, you have three main approaches: (1) Integrated solutions - Eventbrite embeds work with all AI builders, provide professional ticketing, handle payments and check-ins, but charge fees (3.5% + $1.79/ticket). (2) Direct payment - Stripe integration through Webflow, Squarespace Commerce, or custom forms. Lower fees (2.9% + $0.30), but requires manual attendee management. (3) Hybrid approach - Use Eventbrite for initial ticketing, then export attendee list. Combine ease of setup with cost efficiency. For free events, use built-in forms (Typeform, Google Forms) or form builders to collect RSVPs and attendee info. For paid events under 100 attendees, Stripe direct is most cost-effective. For events over 100 attendees, Eventbrite's management features justify the fees."
